# Volunteering vocabulary

## Namespaces
### Ontology Base URI
prefix id:              <https://id.volunteeringdata.io/>
prefix :                <https://ns.volunteeringdata.io/>

### Core W3C ontologies (OWL 2 reserved vocabulary)
prefix rdf:             <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>
prefix rdfs:            <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
prefix owl:             <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#>
prefix xsd:             <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#>

### Other namespaces used
prefix dc:              <http://purl.org/dc/terms/>
prefix skos:            <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#>
prefix time:            <http://www.w3.org/2006/time#>
prefix vcard:           <http://www.w3.org/2006/vcard/ns#>
prefix vann:            <http://purl.org/vocab/vann/>


## Ontology
<https://ns.volunteeringdata.io/>
    a owl:Ontology ;
    rdfs:isDefinedBy <https://ns.volunteeringdata.io/> ;
    dc:issued "2025-11-20"^^xsd:date ;
    vann:preferredNamespacePrefix "volunteering" ;
    vann:preferredNamespaceUri "https://ns.volunteeringdata.io/"^^xsd:anyURI ;
    rdfs:label "Volunteering and Social Action Ontology"@en ;
    rdfs:seeAlso <https://standard.volunteeringdata.io/ontology/> ;
    dc:description "Defines a vocabulary to describe volunteering activities, volunteer-involving organisations and volunteering management systems."@en ;
.


## Datatype Properties
:address
    a owl:DatatypeProperty ;
    rdfs:isDefinedBy <https://ns.volunteeringdata.io/> ;
    rdfs:label "has address"@en ;
.

:charityNumber
    a owl:DatatypeProperty ;
    rdfs:isDefinedBy <https://ns.volunteeringdata.io/> ;
    rdfs:label "has charity number"@en ;
.

:description
    a owl:DatatypeProperty ;
    rdfs:isDefinedBy <https://ns.volunteeringdata.io/> ;
    rdfs:subPropertyOf dc:description ;
    rdfs:label "has description"@en ;
.

:latitude
    a owl:DatatypeProperty ;
    rdfs:isDefinedBy <https://ns.volunteeringdata.io/> ;
    rdfs:label "has latitude"@en ;
.

:longitude
    a owl:DatatypeProperty ;
    rdfs:isDefinedBy <https://ns.volunteeringdata.io/> ;
    rdfs:label "has longitude"@en ;
.

:name
    a owl:DatatypeProperty ;
    rdfs:isDefinedBy <https://ns.volunteeringdata.io/> ;
    rdfs:label "has name"@en ;
.

:title
    a owl:DatatypeProperty ;
    rdfs:isDefinedBy <https://ns.volunteeringdata.io/> ;
    rdfs:label "has title"@en ;
.

:website
    a owl:DatatypeProperty ;
    rdfs:isDefinedBy <https://ns.volunteeringdata.io/> ;
    rdfs:label "has website"@en ;
.


## Concept Scheme
### Scheme Properties
:topConcept
    a owl:ObjectProperty ;
    rdfs:isDefinedBy <https://ns.volunteeringdata.io/> ;
    rdfs:subPropertyOf skos:hasTopConcept ;
    rdfs:domain :ConceptScheme ;
    rdfs:range :Concept ;
    rdfs:label "has top concept"@en ;
.

:ConceptScheme
    a owl:Class ;
    rdfs:isDefinedBy <https://ns.volunteeringdata.io/> ;
    rdfs:subClassOf skos:ConceptScheme ;
    :label "Volunteering Concept Scheme"@en ;
    :description "A taxonomy of concepts related to volunteering activities."@en ;
    :topConcept :Accessibility, :Cause, :Demography, :Language, :Requirement, :Reward, :Skill ;
.

:conceptLabel
    a owl:DatatypeProperty ;
    rdfs:isDefinedBy <https://ns.volunteeringdata.io/> ;
    rdfs:subPropertyOf :label, skos:prefLabel ;
    rdfs:domain :Concept ;
    rdfs:label "concept has preferred label"@en ;
.

:Concept
    a owl:Class ;
    rdfs:isDefinedBy <https://ns.volunteeringdata.io/> ;
    rdfs:subClassOf skos:Concept ;
    :label "Volunteering Concept"@en ;
    :description "Any conceptual information related to volunteering activities."@en ;
.

skos:Concept rdfs:label "SKOS Concept" .

:Accessibility
    a owl:Class ;
    rdfs:isDefinedBy <https://ns.volunteeringdata.io/> ;
    rdfs:subClassOf :Concept ;
    :conceptLabel "Accessibility"@en ;
    :description "Any accessibility information related to volunteering activities."@en ;
.

:Cause
    a owl:Class ;
    rdfs:isDefinedBy <https://ns.volunteeringdata.io/> ;
    rdfs:subClassOf :Concept ;
    :conceptLabel "Charitable Cause"@en ;
    :description "Any charitable cause related to volunteering activities."@en ;
.

:Demography
    a owl:Class ;
    rdfs:isDefinedBy <https://ns.volunteeringdata.io/> ;
    rdfs:subClassOf :Concept ;
    :conceptLabel "Demographic Target"@en ;
    :description "Any demographic information related to volunteering activities."@en ;
.

:Language
    a owl:Class ;
    rdfs:isDefinedBy <https://ns.volunteeringdata.io/> ;
    rdfs:subClassOf :Concept ;
    :conceptLabel "Language"@en ;
    :description "Any language related to volunteering activities."@en ;
.

:Requirement
    a owl:Class ;
    rdfs:isDefinedBy <https://ns.volunteeringdata.io/> ;
    rdfs:subClassOf :Concept ;
    :conceptLabel "Requirement"@en ;
    :description "Any requirement related to volunteering activities."@en ;
.

:Reward
    a owl:Class ;
    rdfs:isDefinedBy <https://ns.volunteeringdata.io/> ;
    rdfs:subClassOf :Concept ;
    :conceptLabel "Reward"@en ;
    :description "Any reward related to volunteering activities."@en ;
.

:Skill
    a owl:Class ;
    rdfs:isDefinedBy <https://ns.volunteeringdata.io/> ;
    rdfs:subClassOf :Concept ;
    :conceptLabel "Skill"@en ;
    :description "Any skill related to volunteering activities."@en ;
.

:ActivityConcept
    a owl:Class ;
    rdfs:isDefinedBy <https://ns.volunteeringdata.io/> ;
    rdfs:subClassOf :Concept ;
    rdfs:label "Activity Concept"@en ;
    :description "Any concept related to a volunteering activity."@en ;
.

:OrganisationConcept
    a owl:Class ;
    rdfs:isDefinedBy <https://ns.volunteeringdata.io/> ;
    rdfs:subClassOf :Concept ;
    rdfs:label "Organisation Concept"@en ;
    rdfs:comment "Any concept related to a volunteer involving organisation."@en .

